Spread/Rest Practice

const fruits = ["apple", "banana"];

const moreFruits = ["cherry", "mango"];

// Merge both arrays using spread

// Create a function that takes any number of fruits and prints them

1. Merge boh arrays using spread:
const fruits = ["apple", "banana"];
const moreFruits = ["cherry", "mango"];

const allFruits = [...fruits, ...moreFruits];
console.log(allFruits);

2.Function that takes any number of fruits:
function printFruits(...items) {
    console.log("Fruits:", items);
}
printFruits("apple", "banana", "mango", "pineapple");


Output:-
[ 'apple', 'banana', 'cherry', 'mango' ]
Fruits: [ 'apple', 'banana', 'mango', 'pineapple' ]
